It does not seem that any key is sent into WSL when it is modified with
Alt.  At the same time, I see the mouse cursor blinking every time I press
Alt+Something.  At first, I thought that it is sending those keys into the
window menu or something like that.  But no window level menu is active.

Based on the change list between rc1 and rc2, I assumed it might be related
to the IME changes.  But the source diff is so small and does not seem to
contain anything suspicious:
https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty/compare/v0.11.0-rc1...v0.11.0-rc2

